<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="External_links">External links</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Being_for_the_Benefit_of_Mr._Kite!&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Alan_W._Pollack" title="Alan W. Pollack">Alan W. Pollack</a>'s <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.icce.rug.nl/~soundscapes/DATABASES/AWP/bftbomk.shtml"><i>Notes on</i> "Being for the Benefit of Mr. Kite!"</a></li>
