<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://kiteprint.com/blogs/news/6943798-other-versions-of-the-mr-kite-poster">Comparisons of modern reproductions of the poster with the original</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.metrolyrics.com/being-for-the-benefit-of-mr-kite-lyrics-beatles.html">Lyrics of this song</a> at <a href="/wiki/MetroLyrics" title="MetroLyrics">MetroLyrics</a></li>
</ul>
